
			
									<h5>Release Date: 19 December 2024</h5>
				
									Neo4j 4.4.40 is a maintenance release with important fixes.
<h3 class="heading-element">Kernel</h3>
<ul>
 	<li>Fix an error that could result in&nbsp;<code>BTREE index has no value capability</code>&nbsp;errors.</li>
</ul>
<div class="markdown-heading">
<h3 class="heading-element">Cypher</h3>
</div>
<ul>
 	<li>Add an internal config setting that can be used to disable a query engine optimization, if needed to prevent a rare bug that can occur with certain complex query plans that can manifest itself as a runtime failure with the error message “java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException: bitIndex &lt; 0”.</li>
</ul>
<div class="markdown-heading">
<h3 class="heading-element">Browser</h3>
</div>
<ul>
 	<li>Add analytics events for browser preview</li>
 	<li>Adding advertisement tile for the new browser ui</li>
</ul>
<div class="markdown-heading">
<h3 class="heading-element">Misc</h3>
</div>
<ul>
 	<li>[CVE-2024-47535] Bump netty from 4.1.111.Final to 4.1.115.Final</li>
</ul>
<h3><b>Bundled Packages:</b></h3>
<ul>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cypher-Shell 4.4.40</span></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">labs/apoc-4.4.0.34-core</span></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">products/bloom-plugin-4.x-2.18.0</span></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">products/neo4j-graph-data-science-2.6.8</span></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">products/neo4j-ops-manager-agent-1.11.2</span></li>
</ul>
